### Variables
@base_url = http://localhost:8000
@job_id = 697f966a-81e7-42e5-89c2-b045b84cb9f0

### Query Document (Non-streaming RAG)
POST {{base_url}}/api/v1/query/{{job_id}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "What are the key obligations mentioned?",
  "top_k": 5
}

### Query Document with Custom Parameters
POST {{base_url}}/api/v1/query/{{job_id}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "Are there any risky conditions or terms?",
  "top_k": 3,
  "collection": "documents"
}

### Stream Query Answer (SSE Streaming)
POST {{base_url}}/api/v1/query/{{job_id}}/stream
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "Explain the named entities in this document",
  "top_k": 5
}
